snippet.title: Friday the 13th: The Game World Gameplay Premier!
snippet.description:
Your first look at early-alpha gameplay from Friday the 13th: The Game! Take an inside look at how you'll control and utilize Jason, as well as witness means of escape and evasion from the counselor's perspective!

Friday the 13th: The Game will release to Xbox One, PS4 and PC in Fall 2016. 

Pre-order now to help with stretch goals: https://friday-the-13th-the-game.backerkit.com/hosted_preorders

www.facebook.com/fridaythe13thgame
www.twitter.com/friday13thgame
www.instagram.com/fridaythe13thgame
www.f13game.com

"Live Until I Die," performed by Crazy Lixx 
www.crazylixx.com
